      <div class="card">
        <h2>Coffee mugs inspired by Sisters</h2>
        <p>These Sisters mugs are great for locals, visitors, cabin weekends, hiking trips, road trips, and anyone who loves the slower mountain-town side of Central Oregon.</p>

        <a class="button" href="https://allthingsbend.etsy.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Shop Sisters Mugs on Etsy
        </a>
      </div>

